The organisers of rAge 2018 have confirmed that the event will take place from 5-7 October 2018. The rAge Expo Twitter account stated that the Ticketpro Dome in Johannesburg will once again play host to South Africa’s biggest gaming exhibition. “Expo tickets on sale from 1 May and NAG LAN tickets on sale 28 July at Computicket,” stated the tweet. rAge 2018 is the largest event in the country focused on PC and console gaming, esports, cosplay, and multiple facets of geek culture – all in one location.